#X text 51 36 The [flanger~] object is a wrap around [fbdelay2~]. The abstraction has a built-in LFO. By default we have a sine \, but you can set it to a triangular wave. You can set the minimum delay value and sweeping amplitude. Check the help file for more details., f 43;
